==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: mystique
<hw>mystique</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An aura of reverence or
mystery stemming from feelings of high value or interest or meaning
surrounding a person or thing; <as>as, the Kennedy
<ex>mystique</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The aura of mystery surrounding the esoteric
knowledge and skills required in certain occupations, or the power of
those possessing those skills; <as>as, the <ex>mystique</ex> of the
astrophysicists</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mytacism</ent>⟦br⟧
